						slowPrintln("There is a yelp from the creature you have surprised. You see something small, no taller than 3 feet, with pink skin and tattered clothes with face that has no nose nor mouth, instead tentacles hang off the thing's face from beneath its massive, pure black eyes. It holds a potato to its chest with a three fingered, clawed hand, shivering.");
					}
